        jTextArea3.setText("The airport apron is the area of an airport where aircraft are parked, unloaded or loaded, refueled, or boarded.  Although the use of the apron is covered by regulations, such as lighting on vehicles, it is typically more  accessible to users than the runway or taxiway. However, the apron is not usually open to the general public  and a license may be required to gain access. ");
